# tCAD

tCAD is a 3D modeling application for a depth enhanced tabletop merging object tracking and user input (on and above the tabletop) in a single system. See class diagram (classDiagram.png)

Compile with LLVM GCC 4.2

## Dependencies / addons

[ofxDelaunay](https://github.com/obviousjim/ofxDelaunay)
[ofKinect](https://github.com/ofTheo/ofxKinect)
[ofxOpenCv](https://github.com/openframeworks/ofxOpenCv)
[ofxOsc](https://github.com/openframeworks/ofxOsc)
[ofxSTL](https://github.com/obviousjim/ofxSTL)
[ofxTuioWrapper](https://github.com/arturoc/ofxTuioWrapper)
[ofxUI](https://github.com/rezaali/ofxUI)
[ofxXmlSettings](https://github.com/openframeworks/ofxXmlSettings)
[ofxGeometry](https://github.com/roxlu/ofxGeometry)
[ofxCarveCSG](https://github.com/paulobala/ofxCarveCSG)

